OL,3,CGraham Linehan accuses police of
OL,4,Ctaking sides after conviction
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FFather Ted co-creator Graham Linehan
OL,8,Fhas accused police of siding with
OL,9,Ftrans rights activists after his
OL,10,Fconviction for damaging a transgender
OL,11,Fcampaigner's mobile phone was
OL,12,Foverturned.
OL,14,FLinehan was caught up in a
OL,15,Fconfrontation with Sophia Brooks
OL,16,Foutside the Battle of Ideas conference
OL,17,Fin Westminster on October 19 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
