OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777701895
OL,3,CGraham Linehan accuses police of
OL,4,Ctaking sides after conviction
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FThe 57-year-old smiled and turned to
OL,8,Fsupporters sitting in the public
OL,9,Fgallery when it was ruled on Friday
OL,10,Fthat his conviction for criminal
OL,11,Fdamage should be overturned.
OL,13,FSpeaking outside Southwark Crown Court
OL,14,Fafter the hearing, the Irish TV writer
OL,15,Fsaid the decision was "very welcome
OL,16,Fbut this case should never have got to
OL,17,Fcourt".
OL,26,@wD@WOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
