FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777701895
OL,3,CGraham Linehan accuses police of
OL,4,Ctaking sides after conviction
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FHe said: "There has been a troubling
OL,8,Fpattern of police forces around the
OL,9,Fcountry to 'believe' trans rights
OL,10,Factivists, time and time again, even
OL,11,Fwhen there has been overwhelming
OL,12,Fevidence that complaints have been
OL,13,Fmade against gender critical
OL,14,Fcampaigners, in bad faith.
OL,16,F"The police have failed in their duty
OL,17,Fto properly and fairly investigate -
OL,18,Fpreferring instead to support one side
OL,19,Fover the other in a debate.
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777701895
OL,3,CGraham Linehan accuses police of
OL,4,Ctaking sides after conviction
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,F"All this has done is erode the faith
OL,8,Fthe public should be able to have in
OL,9,Fthe police.
OL,11,F"We are sick of two-tier policing and
OL,12,FI hope with today's verdict it will
OL,13,Fend."
OL,15,FLinehan added: "I have suffered
OL,16,Fgreatly in my fight to protect women
OL,17,Fand children from what I believe to be
OL,18,Fa dangerous ideology.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@EO]wD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
