OL,3,CGraham Linehan accuses police of
OL,4,Ctaking sides after conviction
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"But I am proud that I have never
OL,13,Fgiven in and I will not do.
OL,15,F"I have been lifted through support
OL,16,Ffrom friends and strangers, from
OL,17,Fwomen's rights groups to London
OL,18,Fcabbies who have taken the time to
OL,19,Fstop and shake my hand."
