OL,7,FHe thanked his legal team and the Free
OL,8,FSpeech Union.
OL,10,FIn November 2025, the Bafta-winning
OL,11,Fwriter was cleared of harassment for
OL,12,Fbranding Brooks a "domestic
OL,13,Fterrorist", a "groomer", and an
OL,14,F"incel".
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
